{"tid":1468970,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實習近平真係幾無政治遠見 當年為本廢書捉人坐洗頭艇 結果今日搞到自己一身蟻","createTime":"2019-08-13T23:46:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T00:53:58.000Z","uid":78336,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2acd9abab3daeb1fa57f99e6c61718623ede1cec","tid":1468970,"uid":78336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T23:46:55.000Z","msg":"雖則話送中係想打擊貪污藏係香港既資產<br />\n但老老實實<br />\n如果當年佢唔係捉林榮基等人坐洗頭艇咁大迴響<br />\n今時今日未必會搞成咁 我諗香港人對d大陸官比人捉返去其實都隻眼開隻眼閉 真係wfc<br />\n捉咁多人坐洗頭艇 就係為左個幾本無咩人睇 無咩人理既小道消息內幕書<br />\n結果搞到個個都知道本習近平情史係真野不特指<br />\n分分鐘中共倒台都係多得呢單野唔少 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以話呢 搞政治無d政治智慧盞害死自己 都見到讀書係幾緊要 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a139878b952f6497296024f28c10d8a6fb4def83","tid":1468970,"uid":78336,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T23:48:38.000Z","msg":"習大大 唔知你有無上連登 希望你睇到呢個po"},{"pid":"498ba548e71c57fd861d1cb50a4e88e02c26c832","tid":1468970,"uid":78336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a139878b952f6497296024f28c10d8a6fb4def83","tid":1468970,"uid":78336,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T23:48:38.000Z","msg":"習大大 唔知你有無上連登 希望你睇到呢個po"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T23:48:49.000Z","msg":"你on9? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16790a03a7720a6422de3c48c519a2fc2efd93ef","tid":1468970,"uid":268373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"498ba548e71c57fd861d1cb50a4e88e02c26c832","tid":1468970,"uid":78336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a139878b952f6497296024f28c10d8a6fb4def83","tid":1468970,"uid":78336,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T23:48:38.000Z","msg":"習大大 唔知你有無上連登 希望你睇到呢個po"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T23:48:49.000Z","msg":"你on9? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T23:49:07.000Z","msg"